    dc:description "Figure 8. Map showing original locality of species of Halicephalobus. H. similigaster (Andrássy, 1952) Andrássy, 1974 (black triangles). Other species of the genus (black circles): 1. H. brevicauda (Mavljanov, 1976) Andrássy, 1984; 2. H. gingivalis (Stefánski, 1954) Andrássy, 1984; 3. H. intermedius (Pokrovskaja, 1964) Andrássy, 1974; 4. H. laticauda Geraert, Sudhaus et al., 1988; 5. H. limuli Timm,1956; 6. H. mephisto Borgonie et al., 2011; 7. H. palmaris (Lordello and De Oliveira, 1963) Andrássy, 1974; 8. H. persicus Shokoohi et al., 2007; 9. H. similigaster (Andrássy, 1952) Andrássy, 1974; 10. H. termitis sp. nov." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/6000715/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

